Quick Order: The uploaded CSV file does not contain a column labelled SKU. Make sure the first column is labelled SKU and that each line in the file contains a SKU value. Then upload the file again.
Hurtigordre: Den opplastede CSV-filen inneholder ikke en kolonne merket SKU. Kontroller at den første kolonnen er merket SKU og at hver linje i filen inneholder en SKU-verdi. Deretter laste opp filen igjen.

Quick Order: You should correct the quantity for the product.
Hurtigordre: Du bør korrigere antallet for produktet.

Quick Order: The SKU is out of stock.
We don't have the quantity you requested.
Hurtigordre: Vi har ikke så mange som du ønsker.

Quick Order: An error occurred. For details, see the error log.
Hurtigordre: An error occurred. For details, see the error log.

Quick Order: The file could not be uploaded because it is in the wrong format. Please select a CSV file to upload.
Hurtigordre: Filen kan ikke lastes fordi den har feil format. Velg en CSV-fil laste opp.

Quick Order: File must be in .csv format and include "SKU" and "QTY" columns
Hurtigordre: Filen må være i CSV-format og inkluderer "SKU" og "Antall" kolonner

Quick Order: Use commas or paragraph to separate SKUs.
Hurtigordre: Bruk komma eller avsnitt for å skille SKUer.

Quick Order: Sorry, something went wrong. You can find out more in the error log.
Hurtigordre: Sorry, something went wrong. You can find out more in the error log.
